65 |title=Wounds|website=Netflix Media Center|accessdate=2019-09-11}}</ref>\n|English\n|}\n\n====2020s====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:100%;\"\n|-\n! Title\n! Genre\n! First screening\n! Length \n! Netflix exclusive region\n!Language\n|-\n| ''Cuties''\n| [[Drama (film and television)|Drama]]\n|2020\n| {{sort|095|1 hour, 35 min.}}\n| Worldwide except France<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/global/netflix-buys-world-rights-to-maimouna-doucoures-sundance-player-cuties-1203467013/|title=Netflix Buys World Rights to Maimouna Doucour\u00e9's Sundance-Player 'Cuties'|website=Variety|date=January 14, 2020}}</ref>\n|French\n|-\n| ''Go Karts''\n| [[Family film]]\n|2020\n| {{sort|102|1 hour, 42 min.}}\n| Worldwide except Australia and New Zealand<ref>{{cite web|url=https://media.netflix.com/en/press-releases/netflix-acquires-coming-of-age-family-film-go-karts-from-aqute-media |title=NETFLIX ACQUIRES COMING-OF-AGE FAMILY FILM GO KARTS FROM AQUTE MEDIA |website=Netflix Media Center|accessdate=2020-01-13}}</ref>\n|English\n|-\n| ''[[La marca del demonio|Mark of the Devil]]''\n| [[Horror film|Horror]]\n| 2020\n| {{sort|082|1 hour, 22 min.}}\n| Seleted territories\n| Spanish\n|-\n| ''[[Miami Bici]]''\n| [[Comedy film|Comedy]]\n| 2020\n| {{sort|098|1 hour, 38 min.}}\n| Seleted territories\n| Romanian/English/French\n|-\n|}\n\n====TBA====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:100%;\"\n|-\n! Title\n! Genre\n! Length \n! Netflix exclusive region\n!Language\n|-\n| ''[[A Boy Called Christmas]]''\n| [[Fantasy film|Fantasy]]\n| TBA\n| Worldwide except UK, Australia, New Zealand, Germany, France and China<ref name=\"abcc\">{{cite web|url=https://media.netflix.com/en/press-releases/studiocanal-netflix-and-blueprint-pictures-a-boy-called-christmas |title=STUDIOCANAL, Netflix and Blueprint Pictures \u2013 A BOY CALLED CHRISTMAS|website=Netflix Media Center|accessdate=2019-04-15}}</ref>\n|English\n|-\n| ''[[:en:The Last Letter from Your Lover|The Last