/netflix-news-masters-of-universe-series.html|title=NETFLIX NEWS: 'MASTERS OF THE UNIVERSE' SERIES ANNOUNCED, 'MODEST HEROES' NETFLIX EXCLUSIVE OUTSIDE NORTH AMERICA|website=animation for adults|date=2019-08-20|accessdate=2019-08-26}}</ref>\n|Japanese\n|-\n| ''[[Munafik 2]]''\n| [[Horror film|Horror]]\n|2018\n| {{sort|104|1 hour, 44 min.}}\n| Selected territories\n|Malay\n|-\n| ''[[My Teacher, My Obsession]]''\n| [[Thriller film|Thriller]]\n|2018\n| {{sort|090|1 hour, 30 min.}}\n| Australia\n|English\n|-\n| ''[[Nothing to Hide (2018 film)|Nothing to Hide]]'' \n| [[Drama (film and television)|Drama]]\n|2018\n| {{sort|093|1 hour, 33 min.}}\n| Worldwide except France\n|French\n|-\n| ''[[Operation Finale]]''\n| [[Drama (film and television)|Drama]]\n|2018\n| {{sort|122|2 hours, 2 min.}}\n| Worldwide excluding U.S.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://media.netflix.com/en/only-on-netflix/292157|title=Operation Finale|accessdate=2018-09-12|website=Netflix Media Center|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180912092018/https://media.netflix.com/en/only-on-netflix/292157|archive-date=2018-09-12|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|English\n|-\n| ''[[Pachamama (film)|Pachamama]]''\n|[[Animated film|Animation]]\n|2018\n| {{sort|071|1 hour, 11 min.}}\n| Worldwide except France, Belgium, Luxembourg, Switzerland and Canada.<ref>{{cite web |title=JUAN ANTIN'S CESAR AWARD NOMINATED ANIMATED FEATURE FILM PACHAMAMA TO DEBUT ON NETFLIX IN JUNE 2019 |url=https://media.netflix.com/en/press-releases/juan-antins-cesar-award-nominated-animated-feature-film-pachamama-to-debut-on-netflix-in-june-2019 |website=Netflix Media Center |accessdate=2019-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190209123854/https://media.netflix.com/en/press-releases/juan-antins-cesar-award-nominated-animated-feature-film-pachamama-to-debut-on-netflix-in-june-2019 |archive-date=2019-02-09 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|English/French\n|-\n| ''[[PASKAL: The Movie|Paskal]]''\n| [[Drama (film and television)|Drama]]\n|2018\n| {{s